  "prompt": "What is the best budget camera phone?",
  "response": "As of the most recent data, selecting the best budget camera phone can depend on your specific needs and preferences. Several budget-friendly phones offer impressive camera performance:\n\n1. **Google Pixel 6a**:\n   - Great camera performance with Google's renowned image processing software.\n   - Clean Android experience with regular updates.\n\n2. **Samsung Galaxy A52s 5G**:\n   - Versatile camera setup including wide-angle and macro lenses.\n   - Good all-around performance and solid build quality.\n\n3. **iPhone SE (2022)**:\n   - Excellent camera for the price, benefits from Apple's image processing.\n   - Compact size and powerful A15 Bionic chip.\n\n4. **Xiaomi Redmi Note 11 Pro**:\n   - High-resolution camera setup.\n   - Generous feature set for the price.\n\n5. **OnePlus Nord N20**:\n   - Balanced camera performance.\n   - Smooth user experience and stylish design.\n\nThese models have been praised for their camera capabilities while maintaining a budget-friendly price. The choice depends on your preferences like ecosystem, design, and additional features beyond the camera.\n\nKeep an eye out for new releases or check the latest reviews, as the landscape for budget-friendly phones is constantly evolving.",
